Name: Average resolution time difference between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median time to transition from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed' versus 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Longest time spent in 'Accepted + Wait' before moving to any next activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E8EF99C100> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest time spent in 'Accepted + Wait' before moving to any next activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Time difference between earliest and latest 'Accepted + Wait' activities within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases that involve 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average elapsed time between 'Accepted + Wait' and the next occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'
